## How to verify it worked (from spec)

```
✓ GET /register → empty form, no error shown
✓ POST valid data → new row in users table → redirect to /
✓ password_hash in DB starts with pbkdf2: or scrypt: (never plaintext)
✓ session["user_id"] set after success
✓ duplicate email → HTTP 200 + friendly error (not 500)
✓ short password → HTTP 200 + error
✓ empty name → HTTP 200 + error
✓ email without @ → HTTP 200 + error
✓ failed POST → name/email pre-filled, password empty
✓ app still starts on port 5001
✓ demo@spendly.com still exists in DB
```

