## Risk areas to watch

| Risk | Why | How to handle |
|---|---|---|
| 500 on duplicate email | IntegrityError uncaught | Wrap INSERT in try/except |
| Session not working | Missing secret_key | Set it before any route |
| Password in form prefill | Security issue | Never pass password back to template |
| SQL injection | String formatting in query | Only `?` placeholders |
| demo user deleted | seed_db modified | Don't touch seed_db at all |